question: Omg I’ve just realized you’ve update a few times since I last read! Ch 5 was where I left off and I’ve noticed the dates of your updates, are you only posting once a month or? Love the story so far! :)
answer: I update whenever I have the chapter finished :) I don’t really have set dates, unfortunately. But I should have more time since it’s the summer term now so hopefully I can pump a chapter out every couple weeks or so! xx
